data.description: Absolutely gorgeous Elko 5 bed, 2 bath, offers 2,032 sq ft, and is located on a CORNER LOT!  Formal living room offers tall vaulted ceilings, hardwood flooring, and large picture window. Kitchen boasts matching white appliances with electric glass top range/oven, white cabinetry, and plenty of counter space with a large breakfast bar. Adjacent to kitchen is dining room area over looking family room just below. Upstairs offers 2 bedrooms, plus the spacious master, and full bath with shower/tub combo and single sink vanity. Just a level down from kitchen area you'll find a spacious family room with an exit onto the absolutely breathtaking massive covered back patio located in the fully fenced and landscaped back yard. Downstairs offers 2 other bedrooms and 2nd full bath complete with single sink vanity, toilet and shower. This home offers central air! Fully landscaped front and back yard. Plenty of parking with 2 car garage, large driveway, and the luxury of all the extra corner lot parking that comes with owning this home. Area for small RV parking on side of home! This home is absolutely move in ready and has everything that makes a house a home.
